@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Link-state: concept (OSPF)

[Router A] as A
[Router B] as B
[Router C] as C
[Router D] as D

A -- B
B -- C
C -- D
A -- D
B -- D

note right of A
  Each router:
  - builds the LSDB (full topology)
  - runs Dijkstra locally
  - derives its routing table
end note

note bottom
  Link-state advertisements are flooded
  to every router within the area.
end note
@enduml
